[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0047","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0047.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0012","title":"Microsoft Internet Information Server 等多款 Web 服务器文件访问限制绕过漏洞","description":"微软 Windows 平台上的 IIS、FrontPage 及 Personal Web Server 等 Web 服务器存在访问控制绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送包含超长文件名的特制请求，绕过服务器的文件访问限制机制，读取本应受限的系统文件或敏感数据。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0、Windows 2000 等系统版本中运行的 IIS 3.0/4.0、Microsoft FrontPage 97/98 及 Personal Web Server 等产品，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.0，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0012"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.700","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Windows 2000 及以上操作系统并部署 IIS 5.0 或更高版本，彻底消除此漏洞。若无法升级，可安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-009 提供的修补程序；另在 IIS 管理器中禁用 8.3 短文件名生成，并使用 URLScan 工具过滤包含连续点号、超长文件名段的请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0012"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0047.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0205","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0205.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0087","title":"IBM AIX Telnet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1/4.2/4.3 版本 Telnet 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向目标系统发送特制的 Telnet 协议数据包，触发服务进程异常崩溃，导致系统完全冻结，合法用户无法登录或访问服务器资源。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.1/4.2/4.3 版本，攻击门槛低，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0087"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.180","remediation":"建议升级 AIX 至 4.3.3 或更高版本，IBM 已在后续维护版本中修复此问题。如无法升级，可在 inetd.conf 中注释 telnet 行并使用 refresh -s inetd 生效，改用 SSH 替代 telnet 服务，同时在防火墙上限制对 23/TCP 端口的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0087","https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0087","http://www.osvdb.org/7992"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0205.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0441","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0441.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0256","title":"War-FTPD 1.65 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"War-FTPD 1.65 在处理用户登录时的密码字段存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务发送超长的密码字符串触发基于栈的缓冲区溢出，导致服务器进程崩溃或在目标系统上执行任意代码。Metasploit 框架已集成该漏洞的利用模块，攻击门槛较低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0256"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.867","remediation":"升级 War-FTPD 至 1.82.00 RC 或更高版本，该版本已修复 Username/Password 栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。如该软件已停止维护，建议迁移至主动维护的 FTP 服务器（如 vsftpd、ProFTPD），并在防火墙限制对 FTP 服务的访问来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/875","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16706","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0256.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0256.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0256","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0256.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0256.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-836r-gprf-7h7h/GHSA-836r-gprf-7h7h.json","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/DDI_warftpd_user_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/3455d6adfb8ec0cc7fbb444ace396770ca5ca6c0/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0441.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0505","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0505.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0304","title":"BSD mmap 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"BSD 系统中 mmap 函数存在权限检查缺陷，属于 kmem 组的本地攻击者可通过操作设备文件实现对内核内存的未授权读写访问，进而提升至 root 权限。该漏洞影响多种 BSD 衍生操作系统，攻击者需先获得本地低权限账户并属于 kmem 组方可利用，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0304"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.750","remediation":"建议立即升级至 FreeBSD 3.0 及以上已修复版本，或应用对应 BSD 厂商的安全补丁。严格限制 kmem 组成员仅限 root 用户，将 /dev/mem 和 /dev/kmem 权限设为 600（仅 root 可读写）。可通过 sysctl -w security.bsd.mmap_of_physmem=0 禁止物理内存映射，并配置内核参数 kern.randompid=1 增强 ASLR 缓解效果。移除不必要的 kmem 组用户，避免被用于内核内存访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0304"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0505.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0510","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0510.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0305","title":"OpenBSD FreeBSD sysctl 源路由 TCP 连接欺骗漏洞","description":"BSD 系统（包括 OpenBSD 2.2 及更早版本、FreeBSD 2.2.5 及更早版本）的 sysctl 设施在设置 dosourceroute 或 forwarding 变量后，未能正确限制源路由数据包的处理，远程攻击者可利用此缺陷伪造 TCP 连接，绕过访问控制机制实施中间人攻击或会话劫持。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 和 FreeBSD 的早期版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0305"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.863","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 2.2.5 以上版本、OpenBSD 至 2.2 以上版本，或在系统配置中设置 sysctl 变量 net.inet.ip.doSourceroute=0 并禁用 IP 转发（sysctl net.inet.ip.forwarding=0），同时在边界防火墙上过滤源路由选项的数据包作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/advisories/sourceroute.txt","http://www.osvdb.org/11502","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/736"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0510.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0491","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0491.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0296","title":"Solaris volrmmount 程序任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统的 volrmmount 程序存在安全漏洞，本地攻击者利用该程序可以读取系统上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用该漏洞，需要本地系统访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0296"],"sources":["cve","nvd"],"published":"1998-02-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 Oracle Sun Security Bulletin 162 提供的补丁程序，或升级到已修复该漏洞的 Solaris 版本。对于已停止支持的 Solaris 版本，建议迁移到受支持的 Solaris 11 或更高版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T16:49:07.408471690+00:00","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/162","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0296"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0491.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0733","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0733.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0486","title":"AOL Instant Messenger 3.5 超链接拒绝服务漏洞","description":"AOL Instant Messenger 3.5 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制的超链接（hyperlink）消息，导致 AIM 客户端在处理该链接时崩溃或停止响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，攻击者无需认证即可触发，影响所有使用 AIM 3.5 版本的用户。由于 AIM 客户端未能正确验证超链接输入，攻击者构造的畸形链接可触发程序异常，导致服务不可用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0486"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-01","updated":"1998-02-01","remediation":"建议立即卸载 AOL Instant Messenger 3.5 客户端，该产品已于 2017 年 12 月 15 日停止服务，官方不再提供安全更新。在浏览器设置中移除 AIM 协议处理程序（aim://）的自动关联，防止恶意超链接自动触发客户端。作为替代方案，迁移至支持端到端加密的现代即时通讯软件（如 Signal、Telegram）。如因历史原因必须使用，建议在防火墙或网络代理层面拦截 aim:// 协议流量作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0733.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0448","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0448.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0264","title":"Miva htmlscript 2.x 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Miva htmlscript 2.x 中的 CGI 程序存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过特制的 URL 路径参数，绕过路径限制访问服务器上的任意文件（如密码文件、配置文件等）。该漏洞影响 htmlscript 2.x 版本，攻击者只需发送 HTTP 请求即可利用，危害等级中等，建议升级至最新版本或禁用该 CGI 程序。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0264"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.847","remediation":"升级 Miva htmlscript 至 3.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复目录遍历问题；如产品已停止维护，应立即从 Web 服务器 cgi-bin 目录中移除 htmlscript CGI 程序。临时缓解措施：在 Apache/Nginx 层面配置规则拦截包含 \"../\" 的 URL 请求，或通过 .htaccess 限制对 htmlscript 脚本的访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0264","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20434","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0264.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0264","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0264.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0264.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h676-3v8p-5vwf/GHSA-h676-3v8p-5vwf.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0264.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.829","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2d13d37d-5c85-422a-bd4e-7e51f93842cc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0448.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0271","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0271.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0125","title":"SGI IRIX mailx 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 系统中的 mailx 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于程序对用户输入的数据长度缺乏充分校验，当攻击者向 mailx 程序传入特制的超长参数时，可触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致程序异常崩溃。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞实现权限提升，获取 root 权限。该漏洞同样影响 RedHat Linux 4.2 和 Solaris 2.6 系统。CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0125"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.563","remediation":"SGI IRIX 用户请安装 SGI 安全公告 19980605-01-PX 提供的 mailx 补丁；RedHat Linux 4.2 用户升级 mailx 到已修复版本；Solaris 2.6 用户安装 Sun 官方 mailx 补丁。临时缓解措施可移除 mailx 的 setuid 位：chmod u-s /bin/mailx。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19312","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0125.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0125","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0125.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0125.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0125.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-295v-8pjh-5r5h/GHSA-295v-8pjh-5r5h.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0271.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0271.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0271.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0049","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0049.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0013","title":"OpenSSH ssh-agent 凭据窃取漏洞","description":"SSH 协议中的 ssh-agent 程序存在凭证泄露漏洞，本地攻击者可通过访问 ssh-agent 进程获取已存储的 SSH 私钥及认证凭证，从而伪装成目标用户登录远程系统。该漏洞影响广泛使用 ssh-agent 的各类 SSH 实现环境，攻击者需要已获得目标系统的本地访问权限方可利用，CVSS 评分 8.4，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0013"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.890","remediation":"升级至支持 SSH2 协议的 OpenSSH_3.0+ 版本并禁用 SSH1 协议（在 sshd_config 中设置 Protocol 2）；同时限制 ssh-agent 的 socket 文件权限（0700）并建议用户在非信任环境中避免使用 ssh-agent 转发功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0013"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0049.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0045","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0045.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0014","title":"多厂商 CDE dtappgather 未授权权限提升漏洞","description":"CDE 桌面环境中的 dtappgather 程序存在文件权限更改漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该程序获取非授权提权访问权限或导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 10.20/11.0、IBM AIX 4.3、SCO Unixware 7.0 及 Sun Solaris 2.6 等操作系统，攻击者通过向 dtappgather 发送特制请求即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0014"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.147","remediation":"联系各操作系统厂商获取对应补丁：HP-UX 安装 PHSS_15068 补丁包，AIX 安装 IY66454 更新，移除 dtappgather 程序的 setuid 权限（chmod 0555 /usr/dt/bin/dtappgather），或在无需 CDE 环境时卸载 dtlogin/CDE 套件以彻底消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/185","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9801-075","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19108","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0014.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0014","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0014.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0014.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0014.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wgf5-r6hp-p33g/GHSA-wgf5-r6hp-p33g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0d95d209-999a-431c-9c33-fdcc7f8c9c24.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0045.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0045.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0045.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0457","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0457.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0271","title":"Progressive Networks Real Video Server 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Progressive Networks Real Video server（pnserver）存在远程拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过发送特制数据包触发该漏洞，导致服务崩溃，影响正常视频流服务。该漏洞利用难度较低，攻击条件简单，但仅影响服务可用性，不会导致数据泄露或权限提升。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0271"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.730","remediation":"建议立即升级至已修复该漏洞的 Progressive Networks RealVideo Server 最新版本，或从网络层面在防火墙上限制对 pnserver 服务端口（默认 TCP 7070）的访问来源，仅允许可信 IP 连接。由于该产品已长期停止维护，强烈建议迁移至现代受支持的流媒体服务器（如 Wowza Streaming Engine 或 Nginx-RTMP）以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0271","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0271.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0271","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0271.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0271.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0271.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6vw2-j8x2-pj9j/GHSA-6vw2-j8x2-pj9j.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/P/pnserver.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82096/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0271.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0457.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0203","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0203.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0086","title":"IBM AIX routed 远程敏感文件修改漏洞","description":"AIX 系统中的 routed 路由守护进程存在访问控制缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的 RIP 路由协议报文，利用该漏洞可修改系统敏感文件，从而获得非授权访问权限或造成系统配置被篡改。该漏洞影响 AIX 操作系统的 routed 服务，攻击者可通过伪造路由更新实施攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0086"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.940","remediation":"升级 AIX 至受支持的最新版本（7.2 TL5/7.3 及以上），该版本已不再使用存在漏洞的 routed 实现。若无法升级，立即停止 routed 服务（`stopsrc -s routed`）并在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释相关行，同时在防火墙侧阻断外部对 UDP 520 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0086"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0203.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0767","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0767.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0513","title":"Linux Kernel ICMP Smurf 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.0/2.1 版本中存在 ICMP Smurf 拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者通过向目标网络的广播地址发送源地址伪造的 ICMP Echo 请求数据包，该网络中的所有主机都会向伪造的源地址（受害者）发送 ICMP Echo 响应，形成流量放大攻击，导致目标系统网络带宽被耗尽而无法提供正常服务。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.0/2.1 及 Digital UNIX、FreeBSD、HP-UX、IBM AIX、NetBSD、Solaris 等多个操作系统版本，攻击条件为目标网络允许定向广播（Directed Broadcast）且未配置相关防护措施。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0513"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:33.307","remediation":"在路由器上禁用 IP 定向广播功能（no ip directed-broadcast），并在各主机操作系统层面禁止响应 ICMP 广播请求（如 Linux 设置 net.ipv4.icmp_echo_ignore_broadcasts=1），同时部署网络入口过滤防止源地址伪造。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0513","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19117","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fec368cf82886628cf7251fa55925507d7e50c60/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0513.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0513","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0513.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4efc2590fd3e232024591793a186ed6577aaac2a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0513.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdec8f567bb266b7b6813bda45223a258023f538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q2cm-72c7-798h/GHSA-q2cm-72c7-798h.json","https://github.com/nbrito/source/blob/7cf72f44a54cbe709dbbac0935c73bf4ba0649d0/c/t50/README.md","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_800_900.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0513.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000249.txt","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0767.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0257","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0257.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0114","title":"Elm elm-2.4 邮件系统本地符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Elm-2.4 邮件客户端中的 filter 命令存在符号链接（symlink）攻击漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在临时目录中创建恶意符号链接，诱使 filter 命令以其他用户的权限执行任意命令或读取敏感文件。该漏洞利用条件为拥有本地账户权限，影响范围包括使用 Elm-2.4 的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级到不受影响的版本或禁用 filter 功能。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0114"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.097","remediation":"立即升级至 Elm 2.4 Patch Level 3 及以上版本，该版本修复了 filter 命令在处理临时文件时的竞态条件问题。若无法升级，建议禁用 filter 命令或移除 elm 的 setuid 权限位以限制 symlink 攻击。长期建议迁移至 mutt 或 alpine 等持续维护的邮件客户端。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0114"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0257.toml"}]